cu.explanation_en: Setting DRB integrity to an invalid enum value will cause integrity configuration errors and prevent secure data transmission.

du.explanation_en: Setting downlink absolute frequency point A to a negative value (-1) will cause frequency configuration errors and prevent proper downlink transmission.
du.explanation_zh: 將下行鏈路絕對頻率點 A 設定為負值 (-1)，會導致頻率配置錯誤，並阻止正確的下行鏈路傳輸。
